tissueExpression.summary: Most of the normal tissues displayed weak to moderate cytoplasmic positivity. Most alveolar cells, lymphoid tissues and bile duct cells were negative.
Most of the normal tissues displayed weak to moderate cytoplasmic positivity. Most alveolar cells, lymphoid tissues and bile duct cells were negative.
Malignant tissues were in general negative or exhibited weak cytoplasmic immunoreactivity. Moderate positivity was mainly observed in colorectal, prostate and liver cancers.
